==English==
===Etymology===
Adjective formed from the noun '''[[Amazon]]''', a river in South America named after a group of women warriors of Greek mythology.

===Adjective===
'''Amazonian'''

# Having to do with the [[Amazon River]] in [[South America]], and the region surrounding the river.

